Package: xcmsVis
Type: Package
Title: Modern Visualization for XCMS Data
Version: 0.99.8
Authors@R: c(
    person("Stanstrup", "Jan", email = "stanstrup@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-0541-7369")),
    person("Anthropic", role = "ctb", comment = "Code generated by Claude AI"))
Description: Provides modern, interactive visualizations for XCMS metabolomics data
    using ggplot2. This package implements ggplot2 versions of XCMS plotting functions,
    enabling interactive plots through plotly and consistent visualization styling.
    Designed as a parallel package to XCMS, maintaining compatibility with both
    XCMSnExp and XcmsExperiment objects and following XCMS conventions for methods
    and object types.
